1
00:00:14,867 --> 00:00:20,305
<i>Connecting old words</i>
<i>that have been used up</i>

2
00:00:21,140 --> 00:00:29,047
<i>I just want to convey</i>
<i>my simple thoughts</i>

3
00:00:29,115 --> 00:00:34,485
<i>That day's faint wind blows away</i>

4
00:00:34,554 --> 00:00:38,615
<i>at the castle ruins of yesterday</i>

5
00:00:39,859 --> 00:00:44,762
<i>I'll laugh with you</i>
<i>and live for the moment</i>

6
00:00:45,498 --> 00:00:52,404
<i>Still that incident</i>
<i>will continue to trouble you, right?</i>

7
00:00:53,806 --> 00:00:57,298
<i>That's why it must be good bye</i>

8
00:00:57,376 --> 00:01:04,339
<i>Leaving nothing behind,</i>
<i>let us share what is left</i>

9
00:01:04,417 --> 00:01:11,482
<i>In time, we'll realize</i>
<i>that it was everything</i>

10
00:01:11,557 --> 00:01:18,224
<i>And sadness will touch our cheeks,</i>
<i>creating a river of tears</i>

11
00:01:18,698 --> 00:01:28,198
<i>Trembling thoughts swept into a vortex</i>
<i>and melting away</i>

12
00:01:39,696 --> 00:01:41,425
<i>Don't forget your objective...</i>

13
00:01:44,567 --> 00:01:45,591
<i>Don't go!</i>

14
00:01:48,505 --> 00:01:49,631
<i>Thank you...</i>

15
00:01:52,942 --> 00:01:54,876
Sasuke...

16
00:02:00,784 --> 00:02:06,086
<i>Formation!</i>
<i>The Sasuke Retrieval Squad!</i>

17
00:02:10,160 --> 00:02:12,060
It's already four o'clock
in the morning...

18
00:02:12,662 --> 00:02:14,892
That Fifth Hokage is
a real slave driver.

19
00:02:14,964 --> 00:02:17,694
She ought to retrieve
the documents she forgot herself...

20
00:02:21,805 --> 00:02:24,205
Huh... What's the matter?

21
00:02:28,244 --> 00:02:29,404
Hey! Wake up!

22
00:02:29,479 --> 00:02:31,811
You'll catch cold if you sleep
in a place like this.

23
00:02:36,453 --> 00:02:37,511
<i>Thank you...</i>

24
00:02:38,922 --> 00:02:39,616
Huh!

25
00:02:39,989 --> 00:02:40,785
Sasuke!

26
00:03:08,451 --> 00:03:09,475
Good work...

27
00:03:12,822 --> 00:03:15,290
Fifth Hokage! You were asleep
just now, weren't you?

28
00:03:15,358 --> 00:03:17,656
When you made us
go to fetch the documents!

29
00:03:17,727 --> 00:03:19,592
And only you got to sleep!

30
00:03:21,764 --> 00:03:23,391
More importantly, Lady Hokage,

31
00:03:23,466 --> 00:03:25,195
there's something
I want to report to you.

32
00:03:25,902 --> 00:03:26,926
What is it?

33
00:03:30,607 --> 00:03:31,904
What did you just say?!

34
00:03:31,975 --> 00:03:32,839
Is that true?!

35
00:03:33,376 --> 00:03:34,138
Yes...

36
00:03:34,577 --> 00:03:38,445
According to Sakura Haruno,
it appears that there's no mistake...

37
00:03:42,085 --> 00:03:45,111
<i>Unbelievable...</i>
<i>That they should already be on the move...</i>

38
00:03:45,822 --> 00:03:49,519
<i>In addition to getting what I want...</i>

39
00:03:49,592 --> 00:03:55,087
<i>This time, I will completely</i>
<i>destroy Leaf Village.</i>

40
00:03:57,167 --> 00:03:59,692
<i>So what that pervert wants...</i>

41
00:04:01,471 --> 00:04:03,371
<i>is the Uchiha's powers, huh...</i>

42
00:04:06,009 --> 00:04:07,374
Izumo! Kotetsu!

43
00:04:08,044 --> 00:04:09,944
There's somebody
I want you to bring here!

44
00:04:12,982 --> 00:04:17,612
Hurry up and eat, Shikamaru!
Your Dad's mission starts today, too!

45
00:04:17,820 --> 00:04:20,152
There's not that much time
for morning training!

46
00:04:20,890 --> 00:04:21,914
OK, OK.

47
00:04:22,525 --> 00:04:23,685
One OK is enough!

48
00:04:25,161 --> 00:04:27,925
<i>Nag, nag, nag from early</i>
<i>in the morning...</i>

49
00:04:29,966 --> 00:04:32,298
I wonder who it could be
so early in the morning?

50
00:04:35,004 --> 00:04:36,562
Hey... Dad...

51
00:04:36,906 --> 00:04:37,668
What is it?

52
00:04:38,274 --> 00:04:41,107
Why did you marry
a hard edged woman like Mom?

53
00:04:43,313 --> 00:04:44,473
Let's see now...

54
00:04:45,248 --> 00:04:48,342
Even though Mom's like that,
she smiles gently sometimes...

55
00:04:48,985 --> 00:04:50,247
Maybe that's why...

56
00:04:54,791 --> 00:04:56,281
Is that the only reason?

57
00:04:58,328 --> 00:04:59,192
Shikamaru!

58
00:05:00,530 --> 00:05:02,862
A messenger of the Fifth Hokage
is here.

59
00:05:08,004 --> 00:05:11,371
Sasuke Uchiha apparently slipped out
of the village late last night.

60
00:05:12,976 --> 00:05:14,273
And... there is almost no mistake

61
00:05:14,344 --> 00:05:17,006
that he is headed for
the Village Hidden in the Sound!

62
00:05:17,313 --> 00:05:19,474
Slipped out?! Why...

63
00:05:20,917 --> 00:05:23,750
Because he was enticed by
that Orochimaru!

64
00:05:25,121 --> 00:05:27,954
W-W-Wait a minute!

65
00:05:28,658 --> 00:05:32,594
Why does Sasuke have to be enticed
by a risky guy like that?!

66
00:05:33,329 --> 00:05:37,390
The reason doesn't matter.
In any case, there's no time.

67
00:05:38,234 --> 00:05:42,000
You will perform your first mission
as a Chunin...

68
00:05:43,239 --> 00:05:45,673
So all I have to do
is bring Sasuke back?

69
00:05:46,409 --> 00:05:48,070
<i>As long as there aren't</i>
<i>any enemies around,</i>

70
00:05:48,144 --> 00:05:50,237
<i>that shouldn't be</i>
<i>too much of a hassle...</i>

71
00:05:51,147 --> 00:05:56,244
Yes... However, not only is time
of the essence on this mission,

72
00:05:56,319 --> 00:05:58,810
but it may turn into something
quite difficult.

73
00:05:59,088 --> 00:05:59,713
Huh?!

74
00:06:00,590 --> 00:06:02,683
There is a strong possibility that

75
00:06:02,759 --> 00:06:05,557
those under the control of Orochimaru
are guiding Sasuke.

76
00:06:06,963 --> 00:06:09,454
<i>This is turning into a real pain</i>
<i>in the neck.</i>

77
00:06:10,099 --> 00:06:17,562
<i>That guy... I held him in high respect</i>
<i>in so many different ways...</i>

78
00:06:19,142 --> 00:06:23,044
In that case, please give me
a four man team

79
00:06:23,112 --> 00:06:25,478
composed only of Jonin and Chunin.

80
00:06:27,150 --> 00:06:28,640
I'm afraid I can't do that...

81
00:06:29,018 --> 00:06:30,383
Huh! Why?!

82
00:06:31,187 --> 00:06:32,586
You already know
the answer to that...

83
00:06:34,090 --> 00:06:39,118
Right now, only the barest minimum
number of Jonin have been left behind

84
00:06:39,195 --> 00:06:41,755
and the others have all
left the village on missions.

85
00:06:45,068 --> 00:06:46,865
Within the next 30 minutes,

86
00:06:46,936 --> 00:06:51,305
I want you to gather all the Genin you
consider the best, and leave this village!

87
00:07:01,417 --> 00:07:03,248
It's a drag but...

88
00:07:03,619 --> 00:07:06,645
I know the guy,
so I just can't just let the matter go.

89
00:07:07,290 --> 00:07:10,054
What shall be, shall be...

90
00:07:13,563 --> 00:07:17,522
There's one guy
I want to recommend.

91
00:07:18,468 --> 00:07:20,368
What! You've gotta be kidding!

92
00:07:22,772 --> 00:07:25,605
You are such a drag starting
so early in the morning...

93
00:07:26,509 --> 00:07:28,909
<i>But why this guy?</i>

94
00:07:32,315 --> 00:07:34,180
<i>That jerk!</i>

95
00:07:35,885 --> 00:07:37,147
Hey, just wait here!

96
00:07:37,220 --> 00:07:38,653
I'll change my clothes immediately!

97
00:07:42,959 --> 00:07:44,586
So, do you have your eye...

98
00:07:44,660 --> 00:07:47,151
on any other guys besides me
who are excellent?

99
00:07:47,730 --> 00:07:48,822
Yeah...

100
00:07:50,500 --> 00:07:52,058
Wake up! Hey!

101
00:07:52,135 --> 00:07:54,467
You said excellent guys, right...

102
00:07:55,805 --> 00:07:57,136
Can't be helped...

103
00:08:00,943 --> 00:08:02,433
Potato chips?

104
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:06,747
They're barbecued meat flavor...
you help out too!

105
00:08:06,883 --> 00:08:07,440
Huh?!

106
00:08:15,425 --> 00:08:15,982
Here he comes!

107
00:08:20,430 --> 00:08:21,692
Even if it <i>is</i> just potato chips,

108
00:08:21,764 --> 00:08:24,733
I won't let anybody else have
the last piece, no matter who you are.

109
00:08:26,569 --> 00:08:30,198
Choji and I have worked as
a team for many years,

110
00:08:30,273 --> 00:08:32,867
so coordinating with him
is easiest for me.

111
00:08:34,710 --> 00:08:36,371
I understand that,

112
00:08:36,446 --> 00:08:39,938
but in this kind of situation,
one would normally solicit Shino first!

113
00:08:40,850 --> 00:08:42,283
Oh, shut up.

114
00:08:49,559 --> 00:08:51,493
Fat chance!

115
00:09:00,803 --> 00:09:05,069
Shino is on a special mission
with his father.

116
00:09:05,908 --> 00:09:08,035
Hey... don't tell me...

117
00:09:08,110 --> 00:09:09,475
Right. He's in.

118
00:09:09,545 --> 00:09:10,739
No way!

119
00:09:13,549 --> 00:09:16,450
I see... Sounds interesting...

120
00:09:17,019 --> 00:09:20,318
It looks like it was worth getting up early
and going for a walk, doesn't it?

121
00:09:20,456 --> 00:09:22,686
Shikamaru, what about the other guys?

122
00:09:23,092 --> 00:09:26,493
I'd like to take my time to look for some,
but we're pressed for time.

123
00:09:27,263 --> 00:09:30,824
If we don't find anybody else
by the time we leave the village,

124
00:09:30,900 --> 00:09:32,128
it will be just us!

125
00:09:33,603 --> 00:09:35,833
It appears that your operation
was a success.

126
00:09:36,372 --> 00:09:36,929
Yeah...

127
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:39,733
Is it okay for you
to be released already?

128
00:09:40,276 --> 00:09:44,474
I was told that I would be able
to undertake light training soon.

129
00:09:45,548 --> 00:09:46,446
I see...

130
00:09:57,793 --> 00:09:58,817
I see...

131
00:09:59,195 --> 00:10:03,325
It's a hassle,
but the more people the better...

132
00:10:06,369 --> 00:10:09,532
<i>Damn... At a time like this, I...</i>

133
00:10:12,141 --> 00:10:16,237
Lee! Do what you need to do.

134
00:10:36,666 --> 00:10:39,794
I'll climb these steps alone
starting tomorrow!

135
00:10:41,037 --> 00:10:41,765
Lee...

136
00:10:44,173 --> 00:10:46,767
I'll be fine! You go!

137
00:10:55,718 --> 00:10:57,117
We're at our time limit!

138
00:11:03,225 --> 00:11:05,921
Well, I've assembled five people...

139
00:11:12,435 --> 00:11:15,632
All right! Everybody, follow me!

140
00:11:20,777 --> 00:11:21,607
Hey...

141
00:11:22,112 --> 00:11:23,511
Hey, Naruto...

142
00:11:23,980 --> 00:11:28,041
I'm supposed to be the squad leader.
Though it sure is a drag...

143
00:11:29,352 --> 00:11:32,583
You really think everything will be okay
if things are left in your hands?

144
00:11:32,655 --> 00:11:34,589
You don't seem very reliable...

145
00:11:35,725 --> 00:11:39,058
What's up with you acting
like the boss, Naruto?

146
00:11:39,396 --> 00:11:42,991
Although being ordered about by
some unmotivated guy like Shikamaru

147
00:11:43,066 --> 00:11:45,261
doesn't sit right with me either...

148
00:11:46,369 --> 00:11:49,270
But Shikamaru is already a Chunin!

149
00:11:49,339 --> 00:11:51,899
We have to follow his orders.

150
00:11:52,442 --> 00:11:55,570
What that means is that
the elders of the village recognized him

151
00:11:55,645 --> 00:11:57,237
as capable of being a leader.

152
00:11:59,082 --> 00:12:03,075
Since that's the case,
come up with some strategy and plan.

153
00:12:03,453 --> 00:12:05,182
From what I heard,
there are enemies

154
00:12:05,255 --> 00:12:07,450
and there's a strong possibility
that they're gonna ambush us.

155
00:12:08,625 --> 00:12:11,185
For a start,
as this is a rescue operation,

156
00:12:11,261 --> 00:12:12,853
we will be in the position
of pursuit.

157
00:12:13,263 --> 00:12:16,960
In other words,
the enemy can easily gain the initiative.

158
00:12:17,901 --> 00:12:21,462
Therefore, I will decide
on a deployment formation

159
00:12:21,538 --> 00:12:23,836
that will respond quickly
to any assault by the enemy.

160
00:12:24,374 --> 00:12:27,502
If you ignore me and
move of your own accord,

161
00:12:27,577 --> 00:12:28,976
we will <i>all</i> die.

162
00:12:32,048 --> 00:12:34,915
We will go in a single file formation.

163
00:12:35,351 --> 00:12:38,912
First of all,
the all-important spearhead will be...

164
00:12:40,390 --> 00:12:42,119
Kiba, that's you!

165
00:12:43,860 --> 00:12:46,055
You and Akamaru go on
walks year round

166
00:12:46,129 --> 00:12:49,064
and are therefore well versed in the terrain
and geography of the Land of Fire.

167
00:12:49,232 --> 00:12:50,824
And since your nose is
very sensitive,

168
00:12:50,900 --> 00:12:52,959
you can track Sasuke
with your sense of smell and,

169
00:12:53,036 --> 00:12:55,630
you can distinguish booby traps
that carry the enemy's scent

170
00:12:55,705 --> 00:12:56,933
which makes them
easy to find...

171
00:12:57,841 --> 00:13:01,538
And moreover, you and Akamaru as
a pair will be extremely efficient

172
00:13:01,611 --> 00:13:05,980
in compensating for the weakness
of a single file formation to assault.

173
00:13:07,517 --> 00:13:10,543
And... second in line will be me,
the squad leader.

174
00:13:11,121 --> 00:13:13,954
I can give orders
as required in any situation

175
00:13:14,023 --> 00:13:16,082
from my position
directly behind Kiba

176
00:13:16,159 --> 00:13:19,959
and can give orders to those behind me
using only hand signals.

177
00:13:20,563 --> 00:13:23,964
And in the middle...
in the number three position is Naruto.

178
00:13:25,468 --> 00:13:27,561
The middle position is
the best for you,

179
00:13:27,637 --> 00:13:29,696
since you're capable
of executing quick moves

180
00:13:29,772 --> 00:13:32,866
and are able to respond immediately
to anything in front or behind.

181
00:13:33,309 --> 00:13:37,075
You're the cornerstone...
And you have Shadow Clone, too.

182
00:13:38,414 --> 00:13:41,042
And fourth in line is Choji.

183
00:13:41,151 --> 00:13:44,518
You. You don't have speed,

184
00:13:44,587 --> 00:13:47,055
but your ability to strike is the best
among the squad members.

185
00:13:47,357 --> 00:13:50,724
Line leader Kiba, I, and Naruto
will launch a surprise attack

186
00:13:50,793 --> 00:13:52,522
and I'll use you to launch
the deciding blow.

187
00:13:52,795 --> 00:13:54,626
In other words, your role is
to attack the routed enemy.

188
00:13:55,565 --> 00:13:57,726
And then, on the tail end
will be you, Neji...

189
00:13:58,268 --> 00:14:02,398
You are assigned to
the most difficult position of rear lookout.

190
00:14:02,906 --> 00:14:04,931
You will use your Byakugan
to constantly check

191
00:14:05,008 --> 00:14:06,566
that there are no loopholes
in the ranks.

192
00:14:11,881 --> 00:14:14,008
Got it? Take a careful look at this.

193
00:14:20,190 --> 00:14:23,956
Use this diagram to verify
the radius of your assigned watch.

194
00:14:24,894 --> 00:14:26,623
Kiba watches the front,

195
00:14:26,696 --> 00:14:29,096
I'm responsible for
a wide forward view,

196
00:14:29,899 --> 00:14:34,461
Naruto watches left, Choji right,
and Neji...

197
00:14:34,938 --> 00:14:38,271
Using your Byakugan,
you cover the entire area to the rear.

198
00:14:39,475 --> 00:14:43,138
I want to familiarize myself
with our current military potential.

199
00:14:43,680 --> 00:14:47,377
Let me check all the Ninja equipment
each of you currently has...

200
00:14:47,817 --> 00:14:49,580
I will commit that
to memory straight away.

201
00:14:50,220 --> 00:14:51,653
Any questions?

202
00:14:54,724 --> 00:14:57,124
<i>Even though he just assembled</i>
<i>his men a short while ago,</i>

203
00:14:57,193 --> 00:14:59,855
<i>he's already created</i>
<i>the best possible formation...</i>

204
00:15:00,964 --> 00:15:04,923
If not, I want to tell you
the most important thing last.

205
00:15:09,072 --> 00:15:12,940
Sasuke and I aren't close friends.

206
00:15:13,176 --> 00:15:15,201
In fact, I don't particularly like him.

207
00:15:20,350 --> 00:15:24,116
However, he is also a Shinobi belonging
to the Village Hidden in the Leaves.

208
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:25,514
He is a comrade!

209
00:15:25,922 --> 00:15:27,981
Therefore, I will put my life
on the line to help him!

210
00:15:28,725 --> 00:15:30,317
That's the way
of the Leaf Village.

211
00:15:31,327 --> 00:15:35,661
In this case, even I can't just sit back
and be a sluggard.

212
00:15:37,634 --> 00:15:40,398
Because I am responsible
for your lives.

213
00:15:44,340 --> 00:15:49,539
Wow... You're acting kind of
like a Chunin, aren't you?!

214
00:15:51,347 --> 00:15:54,441
Okay then, as soon as he's checked
our Ninja tools, we'll depart.

215
00:15:55,084 --> 00:15:56,711
Everybody, take out your Ninja tools.

216
00:16:05,695 --> 00:16:08,960
<i>Sasuke wouldn't fall victim</i>
<i>to that kind of guy's enticement...</i>

217
00:16:09,032 --> 00:16:11,125
<i>He's already</i>
<i>a really powerful guy,</i>

218
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:15,330
<i>so he wouldn't need to do</i>
<i>that kind of thing! I guarantee it!</i>

219
00:16:19,208 --> 00:16:22,575
<i>Damn... Why, Sasuke...?!</i>

220
00:16:23,446 --> 00:16:25,380
All right! Let's go!

221
00:16:25,448 --> 00:16:26,142
Wait!

222
00:16:32,088 --> 00:16:33,020
Sakura!

223
00:16:34,590 --> 00:16:37,126
I heard the whole story
from Lady Hokage.

224
00:16:37,126 --> 00:16:39,492
I'm sorry, but I can't take you along
on this mission.

225
00:16:41,230 --> 00:16:44,791
Even you weren't able
to convince Sasuke, right?

226
00:16:46,669 --> 00:16:50,765
All that can be done now is for us
to use force to convince him...

227
00:16:51,441 --> 00:16:54,774
Sakura, your role in this has ended.

228
00:16:58,581 --> 00:17:01,846
Which means, Sakura,
that you and Sasuke?!

229
00:17:06,789 --> 00:17:07,721
<i>Sakura...</i>

230
00:17:17,800 --> 00:17:23,067
Naruto... This is a...
once in a lifetime request...

231
00:17:24,807 --> 00:17:28,971
Please bring...
please bring Sasuke back.

232
00:17:30,546 --> 00:17:36,712
I couldn't do it!
I wasn't able to stop Sasuke!

233
00:17:37,987 --> 00:17:42,287
At this point, the only person
who would be able to stop Sasuke...

234
00:17:42,358 --> 00:17:44,622
who would be able to save him...

235
00:17:45,762 --> 00:17:48,663
is you... Naruto...

236
00:17:59,308 --> 00:18:02,903
You like Sasuke so much,
don't you, Sakura?

237
00:18:04,480 --> 00:18:08,246
I understand to my very core

238
00:18:08,718 --> 00:18:11,186
how painful it must be
for you right now, Sakura.

239
00:18:14,891 --> 00:18:18,725
<i>Sakura, there's one thing</i>
<i>I want to ask you.</i>

240
00:18:18,795 --> 00:18:19,727
<i>Huh?</i>

241
00:18:20,363 --> 00:18:22,957
<i>How do you feel about...Naruto?</i>

242
00:18:25,067 --> 00:18:28,400
<i>Thwarting someone's love seems</i>
<i>to have become natural to him.</i>

243
00:18:28,938 --> 00:18:31,532
<i>He actually seems to be enjoying</i>
<i>my suffering.</i>

244
00:18:32,008 --> 00:18:35,239
<i>Naruto doesn't understand</i>
<i>the least thing about me.</i>

245
00:18:35,812 --> 00:18:36,870
<i>He's just annoying.</i>

246
00:18:50,092 --> 00:18:53,061
Naruto... thank you...

247
00:18:54,697 --> 00:19:00,135
I'll bring Sasuke back without fail!
I promise that on my life!

248
00:19:03,272 --> 00:19:06,264
<i>You always understood me...</i>

249
00:19:07,477 --> 00:19:10,207
<i>You always helped me...</i>

250
00:19:15,017 --> 00:19:15,949
<i>Naruto...</i>

251
00:19:21,424 --> 00:19:23,153
Hey, hey, Naruto!

252
00:19:23,226 --> 00:19:26,627
You really think you're gonna be okay
saying that kind of thing?!

253
00:19:26,796 --> 00:19:29,731
Sure! I will not go back on my word.

254
00:19:30,066 --> 00:19:31,863
That's my Way of the Ninja!

255
00:19:32,268 --> 00:19:35,396
All right! Let's hurry up and go!

256
00:19:35,671 --> 00:19:39,732
We've lost a little time...
Let's hurry!

257
00:19:40,276 --> 00:19:40,833
OK!

258
00:19:57,026 --> 00:20:00,052
Naruto struck the pose of
a nice guy as he said that...

259
00:20:00,897 --> 00:20:02,091
It'll all be all right now.

260
00:20:03,199 --> 00:20:05,861
I'm positive...
I'm positive that it will all go well!

261
00:20:23,853 --> 00:20:27,118
Master Sasuke... Around here will do,
don't you think?

262
00:20:27,189 --> 00:20:29,680
We've already exited
the Village Hidden in the Leaves.

263
00:20:31,160 --> 00:20:32,058
What is that?

264
00:20:33,095 --> 00:20:34,323
To tell you the truth,

265
00:20:34,397 --> 00:20:37,958
Orochimaru has given us
one important task...

266
00:20:39,201 --> 00:20:41,226
So... what is it?

267
00:20:58,854 --> 00:21:02,381
It will be necessary for you
to die once...

268
00:21:13,135 --> 00:21:20,234
<i>Once in a long while, once in a while</i>

269
00:21:20,376 --> 00:21:25,905
<i>The remnants of a person</i>
<i>broken by dreams</i>

270
00:21:26,082 --> 00:21:31,145
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

271
00:21:34,457 --> 00:21:41,454
<i>Clinging to the Divine,</i>
<i>clinging to Buddha</i>

272
00:21:41,530 --> 00:21:47,059
<i>The remnants of a person crying</i>

273
00:21:47,470 --> 00:21:51,031
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

274
00:21:52,708 --> 00:21:55,768
<i>Rendezvous with a happy dance circle</i>

275
00:21:55,845 --> 00:21:59,645
<i>This is my victory pose, round and around</i>
<i>(round around)</i>

276
00:21:59,982 --> 00:22:02,917
<i>Shake shake shake</i>
<i>Let's look</i>

277
00:22:02,985 --> 00:22:07,115
<i>With a bye bye rhythm that never ends</i>

278
00:22:16,298 --> 00:22:21,395
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

279
00:22:23,339 --> 00:22:26,604
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

280
00:22:27,009 --> 00:22:30,206
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

281
00:22:30,479 --> 00:22:34,472
<i>Look like a mountain</i>

282
00:22:38,187 --> 00:22:40,849
From here on up, there's more danger
of traps and ambushes.

283
00:22:41,057 --> 00:22:42,888
- Stay alert and use all your senses.
- Roger that!

284
00:22:43,092 --> 00:22:45,219
- Find the enemy before he gets you.
- You can count on me!

285
00:22:45,294 --> 00:22:47,228
- And any signs of the enemy
- Right!

286
00:22:47,396 --> 00:22:49,091
Say, are you listening?!

287
00:22:49,165 --> 00:22:51,599
Not to worry.
No matter who the enemy may be,

288
00:22:51,667 --> 00:22:54,295
I'll thrash him with
my new technique!

289
00:22:54,370 --> 00:22:57,703
I'm a fool to
even attempt to explain.

290
00:22:58,641 --> 00:23:02,441
Next time:
"Sound vs. Leaf"
